## ❀ Purpose of This Section ────୨ৎ────────୨ৎ────

The purpose of this folder is to keep all extra materials organized in one place. These resources are not part of the main technical sections, but they support our engineering explanation by showing testing evidence, design progress, code improvements, and future documentation plans.

| Resource Type | Why It Helps |
| :--- | :--- |
| **Testing graphs** | Show measurable evidence of improvement. |
| **Code metrics** | Support the decision to simplify the software. |
| **Sensor data** | Show how lighting, placement, and calibration affected readings. |
| **3D model notes** | Prepare space for future digital reconstruction files. |
| **Testing logs** | Help connect practice results with design changes. |
| **Reference links** | Make the repository easier to navigate. |

